Package tilda.db

Class MasterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • tilda.db.MasterFactory
  • public class MasterFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    LDH-NOTE This class helps issue an arbitrary select query against any object currently active in the system. Although its main method takes in a String, it is validated against the TildaSQL grammar and will not execute unless it passes parsing + validation.
    Author:
    ldh
